From A.D. 1454-5‚ when the series of Court Rolls ceases, there are no records of the Borough Court preserved until A.D. 1481-82. During the interval the system of keeping the records had changed ; the proceedings were now entered in paper books in a very careless style instead of being neatly written on parchment rolls as thereto- fore.
